General Information

Collagen Power for oral consumption berry flavour

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional

Common Uses

Collagen is an abundant protein in the human body, and most abundan component of extracellular matrix. A reduction in total collagen production is a characteristic of ageing skin. Hydrolysed Collagen when taken orally can contribut to maintain skin structure. Incorporating collagen intake in routine can provide an inside and out solution to your skincare. Wagner Bioactive Collagen Powder is berry flavoured and is an easy way to increase your collagen intake.

Ingredients

Ingredients: Hydrolysed collagen, Dextrose, Citrus bioflavonoids extract, Vitain C, Vegetable gum (Guar gum) Natural flavours Beet red, Grape seed extract Sweetener (Thaumatin)

Directions

Take 5 grams daily (2 scoops) dissolved in 100ml water or beverage of your choice, or as directed by your healthcare professional.
